Interface StatisticVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StatisticCompiler

    public interface StatisticVisitor
    The StatisticVisitor interface create a visit method for each visitable object. It is implemented by the statistic compiler.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pierre Averous, Nicolas Topuz
